Summary: We were taking pics of a spinning and colorful "star" that kept brightening and dimming
divs: Sighting DetailsMy mom and myself were looking at a strange spinning "star" that kept changing colors. It kept going further away and coming closer, then brightening and then dimming. This went on for 4 plus hours starting at around 10pm. I took several pics and then downloaded them onto my computer. The pics were not altered in any way except to sharpen the image and crop it closer to see it better. What do you think it could be????
